## The math

The mathematical results in this repository â€” the Goldberg-Coxeter
construction, Euler's theorem on convex polyhedra, the C60 closure
invariants, the {2,3,5} Coxeter constraint â€” are not owned by anyone.
They were proved by humans who are mostly dead and belong to all of us.

This repository is a computational implementation of those results.
The implementation is mine. The math is humanity's.

